snippet.title: Martin DeCoder
snippet.description:
For more than 5 years, I've worked as an External Lecturer. 

I have a BA in Linguistics and Media Studies and an MA in Media Studies.

Among my primary specialties are: 1) conversation analyses of everyday conversations, TV interviews, and pretty much everything that involves spoken language; 2) audiovisual analyses of written and visual material: corporate communication, political branding, documentaries, movies, and TV shows.

The content of this channel reflects my specialties. If this kind of content interests you too, please LIKE, SHARE & SUBSCRIBE.

For business inquiries (media, universities, collaborations), send an email to: decoder.department@gmail.com. 
Typical response time: 1-2 week(s).
